{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-post-templates-project-post-jsx","path":"/projects/avatar-customizer","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<div class=\"block\"><h2>Details üìù</h2><h2><a href=\"https://rhiannanberry.github.io/Avatar-Customizer\">Play with the avatar customizer here!</a></h2><h4><a href=\"https://github.com/rhiannanberry/Avatar-Customizer\">Code Repository</a></h4><h3>Description</h3><p>Web-based avatar customizer to be used on <strong>Mozilla Hubs</strong><sup id=\"fnref-1\"><a href=\"#fn-1\" class=\"footnote-ref\">1</a></sup>. I developed this as a part of my research with <strong>AEL</strong><sup id=\"fnref-2\"><a href=\"#fn-2\" class=\"footnote-ref\">2</a></sup>. It's still in active development, too!</p><h3>Goals</h3><p>The goal here was to let Hubs users create a more custom and humanoid avatar than the pre-existing robotic avatars readily available on Hubs. It needed to have an easy workflow, and a broad set of options to support a variety of people, as our research lab was preparing for two VR conferences that would <em>take place</em> in VR. </p><p>Also, I wanted to dip my toes into \"real\" open source development for the first time, as this tool would have the opportunity to be a part of Mozilla's codebase. </p><h3>Accomplishments</h3><p>Accomplished almost everything I was going for! We got to see lots of people repping custom avatars at the <strong>IEEEVR 2020 conference</strong><sup id=\"fnref-3\"><a href=\"#fn-3\" class=\"footnote-ref\">3</a></sup>, and I'm told many are still using them months later :) </p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=avatar%20(%40rhiannan_online)&#x26;src=typed_query&#x26;f=image\">Here's</a> just a few Tweets I got of people sharing them with me!</p><p>The project is still in progress, though, so there is still plenty of ways to improve and expand! Once my hiatus is over, I plan on vastly expanding available hairstyles, facial hair, and accessories, and improving UI and code-readability.</p></div>\n<div class=\"block\"><h2>Screenshots üì∑</h2><p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 495px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"avatar customizer 1\"\n        title=\"avatar customizer 1\"\n        src=\"/static/fad780f4a630b7d6745cdb0883e51b10/68bae/avatar-customizer-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fad780f4a630b7d6745cdb0883e51b10/072e7/avatar-customizer-1.png 240w,\n/static/fad780f4a630b7d6745cdb0883e51b10/9aebd/avatar-customizer-1.png 480w,\n/static/fad780f4a630b7d6745cdb0883e51b10/68bae/avatar-customizer-1.png 495w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p><p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 924px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"avatar customizer 2\"\n        title=\"avatar customizer 2\"\n        src=\"/static/c055bbb01f315ce348bd6a6ed5fcda90/8643c/avatar-customizer-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c055bbb01f315ce348bd6a6ed5fcda90/072e7/avatar-customizer-2.png 240w,\n/static/c055bbb01f315ce348bd6a6ed5fcda90/9aebd/avatar-customizer-2.png 480w,\n/static/c055bbb01f315ce348bd6a6ed